    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! This car has been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so you can expect a smooth ride and plenty of great miles ahead. It\u2019s perfect for anyone looking for a quality vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles! \u2728",
