    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in wonderful shape! It drives super smoothly and has been really well-loved, making it perfect for your daily commutes or fun weekend adventures. I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
