      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, a quintessential driver\u2019s machine featuring the legendary S54 inline-six powerplant equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, providing tactile gear selection and delivering power to the rear wheels through the factory M-Variable Lock limited-slip differential. The chassis has been properly sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the engine maintains excellent compression and a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Ideal for the purist seeking hydraulic steering feedback and the visceral intake note of a high-revving, naturally aspirated masterpiece.",
